  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "In these models, GCNs are used to process molecular structures of drugs or knowledge graphs containing various entities and relationships.",
    "This ability to capture rich information from different networks makes GCNs a good choice for modeling complex biological relationships (Wang et al. 2022b; Zhang et al. 2023; Liu and Xie 2021).",
    "The PRODeepSyn (Wang et al. 2022b) model leverages the GCN to construct gene hidden states based on the PPI network.",
    "Zhang et al.",
    "(Zhang and Tu 2022) emphasize the pivotal role of GCNs in extracting valuable information from the constructed KG."
  ],
